{
  "stem": "25809.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We couldn't get out of the country.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had tried to get out of the country when the war broke out and drove to [NON-ENGLISH], trying to see if we could board a vessel.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We tried to board a vessel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Fortunately, we didn't board it because we found out later on it was torpedoed by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't know-- in, in today's day and age, if I would have had to cross the border, I would figure out a way at my age to cross the border.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But my father and mother were not of the type of people that-- hey, they were a sedate type people in their 40s, 45 years old or so.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were not very active.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They-- climbing a mountain wouldn't cross their mind.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they kind of were stuck.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They, they couldn't move.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're-- they were paralyzed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Later on, this whole thing, to avoid being paralyzed, manifested itself for me that I became totally enchanted with sailing of boats.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had my own boats with the idea in mind that, whatever happened in this world, I would have my own transportation, and I would be able to transport myself from point A to point B away from a bad area so that I would not be stuck like everybody else was during the war.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I would be independent.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I executed that totally, that I would be totally independent.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then later on became old enough that I felt it wasn't necessary anymore because in this day and age, wherever you go, if there's a nuclear bomb, forget it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I would be wiped out, anyhow, wherever I would be.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But anyhow, maybe I'm getting ahead of things here.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
